{"tid":2119003,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人每朝一起身就有痰、喉嚨痛","createTime":"2020-07-22T00:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T10:52:25.000Z","uid":199048,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9c829c169cd1e225d8be6baa3a9664171e416e19","tid":2119003,"uid":199048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:48:00.000Z","msg":"過咗幾個鐘就好返啲，但第二朝又再黎<br />\n<br />\n持續咗一年半<br />\n<br />\n同過唔同醫生講幾次<br />\n<br />\n個個都話鼻水倒流好正常，話側瞓會好啲<br />\n<br />\n半年前呼吸道大病過一次<br />\n<br />\n之後每朝啲痰變埋有啲綠色咁<br />\n<br />\n綠色咗半年<br />\n<br />\n有時仲會半夜五點喉嚨痛醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇清知道咩事？"},{"pid":"640fc829ffc8fd38873f41cf29434dcf03a3ca61","tid":2119003,"uid":199048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:50:52.000Z","msg":"我估應該真係關鼻水倒流事<br />\n<br />\n因為我企直個人就冇事<br />\n<br />\n瞓低就有事<br />\n<br />\n側瞓會好啲啲（都好嚴重）<br />\n<br />\n平瞓就最嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9d0c160c0b727c5acc0ae40f6df98626ced847","tid":2119003,"uid":78599,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"640fc829ffc8fd38873f41cf29434dcf03a3ca61","tid":2119003,"uid":199048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:50:52.000Z","msg":"我估應該真係關鼻水倒流事<br />\n<br />\n因為我企直個人就冇事<br />\n<br />\n瞓低就有事<br />\n<br />\n側瞓會好啲啲（都好嚴重）<br />\n<br />\n平瞓就最嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:52:57.000Z","msg":"竟然有同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我每一朝逼完啲痰出黎就成都會無事 <br />\n<br />\n但一訓醒返就有返"},{"pid":"0327208b4a2359f46a8105e58d68debd83dedcf6","tid":2119003,"uid":221285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:53:39.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但d痰唔係綠色"},{"p